    "causal_summary": "Smart-routing umbrella skill for application code work. Detects the project stack from marker files (Webflow, React/Next.js, Go) then classifies intent and loads stack-aware resources. Stacks: WEBFLOW (LIVE \u2014 Webflow / vanilla animation web with motion.dev / GSAP / Lenis / HLS / Swiper / FilePond signals), NEXTJS (STUB \u2014 scaffolded for a future Next.js 14 App Router project paired with vanilla-extract + motion v12 + react-hook-form/zod + react-aria + Untitled UI + next-themes), GO (STUB \u2014 scaffolded for a future gin + sqlc + pgx + Postgres + go-playground/validator + golang-jwt service). Cross-stack pairing doc captures the React\u2194Go API contract, JWT handoff, error envelope shape, CORS, and deploy topology \u2014 preserved as canonical contract content (not a stub). NEXTJS and GO subfolder content was placeholder-filled in packet 056 (absorbed 057) (2026-04-30); populate when real projects are wired in. Other stacks (Node.js without React/Next, React Native, Swift) fall through to UNKNOWN \u2014 this skill does not own them.",
